{"tid":160778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【十二宮性侵案】強姦情婦未成年女兒　男子13項罪名成立","createTime":"2017-03-18T04:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T08:32:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d62ac62c2b96d5a59520dfd90970539e164d8bc","tid":160778,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"(12:58)<br />\n2017/3/17<br />\n<br />\n已婚的士司機李國明（50歲）藉詞「消災解劫」做「黃道十二宮」法事，被控侵犯情婦的兩名未成年女兒。案件經歷近一個月審訊，法官昨完成引導陪審團，由5男2女組成的陪審團退庭商議近11小時後，今午裁定被告1項猥褻侵犯罪罪成、2項強姦罪罪成及10項以虛假藉口促致另一人作非法的性行為罪成，而1項以虛假藉口促致另一人作非法的性行為罪名不成立。被告還押等待判刑。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n法官將案件押後至4月10日聽取求情及判刑，待索兩事主的創傷報告及被告的臨牀心理學家報告。<br />\n<br />\n被告聞裁決時，起初表現平靜，但當首席陪審員逐一宣讀裁決結果時，被告開始低頭、念念有詞及搖頭等等。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170317/s00001/1489726308904#sthash.DPK4c7lZ.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170317%2Fs00001%2F1489726308904%23sthash.DPK4c7lZ.dpuf&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=2742fd07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170317%2Fs00001%2F1489726308904%23sthash.DPK4c7lZ.dpuf&h=16cb2af1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170317/s00001/1489726308904#sthash.DPK4c7lZ.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"98c512474a02f1dd20143d06947b252045d2e116","tid":160778,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12db3d868f21e70bfbbe2136f5ff98a5452d13c4","tid":160778,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"點解可以有呢d人既存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307020f2cb08be2e26812898837f21ac3ee7a71b","tid":160778,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,